metadata.name: Our mothers , our soil
metadata.description: Like the ground beneath our feet. Our Mothers are the firtile ground in which we are grown from. Their undying love and care hang upon them like crowns. Forever providing nourishment and healing to her family like pots of water. It's her pride to be selfless, just like soil. Forever committed to growing others and being the ground upon which nations are built. Our Mothers, Our soil
